## Display counter for Ancient Debris gathered
scoreboard objectives add mwc_debris_gathered dummy "Ancient Debris Gathered"

## track raw stats for ancient debris
scoreboard objectives add debris_picked_up minecraft.picked_up:minecraft.ancient_debris
scoreboard objectives add debris_dropped minecraft.dropped:minecraft.ancient_debris
scoreboard objectives add debris_used minecraft.used:minecraft.ancient_debris
